yday experience, and the nature of subjectivity.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Sep 2020) 0aGames in art. 0aPaintingxPsychological aspects. 0aPlay in art. 0aPsychoanalysis and art. 0aSurrealism. 0aSymbolism in art. 4aAPHI. 4aArt History Publication Initiative. 7aART / History / Modern (late 19th Century to 1945).2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDUK eBook-Package 2019z978311069632540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781478003434zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781478003434423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781478003434.jpg  a978-3-11-069632-5  DUK eBook-Package 2019b2019  aEBA_DUK_ALL  aEBA_DUK_EALL  aEBA_DUK_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles